´´´mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant SA as Service A (Order)
    participant SB as Service B (Inventory)

    C->>G: 1. Request to create order (POST /orders)
    activate G
    G->>SA: 2. Routing: create order
    activate SA
    SA->>SB: 3. Check item availability
    activate SB
    SB-->>SA: 4. Item is available
    deactivate SB
    SA->>SA: 5. Save order to DB
    SA-->>G: 6. Order successfully created
    deactivate SA
    G-->>C: 7. HTTP 201 Created (Response)
    deactivate G
